data.description: YOUR dream home! TRUE meaning of move-in ready meets prime location! This immaculate 3-B/ 2 Bath/ 2-CG offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. This stunning haven boasts a brand NEW METAL ROOF (10/2023), INCLUDING SHED, ensuring durability and style for years to come. Step inside to discover a beautifully renovated interior (ALL DONE 2023) boasting ALL NEW laminate flooring, NEW bathrooms with NEW SS kitchen appliances & NEWER GARAGE DOOR (2021). The inviting open-concept adorned with vaulted ceilings, creating a spacious and welcoming lifestyle WITH NEWLY opened kitchen. Outside, the fenced yard surrounds a MASSIVE screened-in patio with pass-through window from kitchen perfect for entertaining. Mins to shopping and dining destinations, schools, colleges and major HWYS.
